						</svg>
					</div>
					<div class="exp-text">
						<span class="exp-label">Octapar: A Framework for Multi-Modal, Balanced User Grouping using Weighted Attentional Embeddings and Assignment-Based Clustering</span>
						<span class="exp-tag">23rd the company · 2025</span>
